		<title>新竹青草湖×航海王盛大啟航　開啟最熱血的秋季冒險！</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/10/27/%e6%96%b0%e7%ab%b9%e9%9d%92%e8%8d%89%e6%b9%96x%e8%88%aa%e6%b5%b7%e7%8e%8b%e7%9b%9b%e5%a4%a7%e5%95%9f%e8%88%aa%e3%80%80%e9%96%8b%e5%95%9f%e6%9c%80%e7%86%b1%e8%a1%80%e7%9a%84%e7%a7%8b%e5%ad%a3/</link>
		
