		<title>經濟部攜手藝康台灣推動智能水務、食安預防與生技醫療升級　共促永續產業新動能</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/10/27/%e7%b6%93%e6%bf%9f%e9%83%a8%e6%94%9c%e6%89%8b%e8%97%9d%e5%ba%b7%e5%8f%b0%e7%81%a3%e6%8e%a8%e5%8b%95%e6%99%ba%e8%83%bd%e6%b0%b4%e5%8b%99%e3%80%81%e9%a3%9f%e5%ae%89%e9%a0%90%e9%98%b2%e8%88%87%e7%94%9f/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Mon, 27 Oct 2025 03:48:04 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[其他]]></category>
