		<title>WePlay攜手Care Bears™打造萬聖節嘉年華　以暖心魔法點亮秋日派對</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/10/27/weplay%e6%94%9c%e6%89%8bcare-bears%e6%89%93%e9%80%a0%e8%90%ac%e8%81%96%e7%af%80%e5%98%89%e5%b9%b4%e8%8f%af%e3%80%80%e4%bb%a5%e6%9a%96%e5%bf%83%e9%ad%94%e6%b3%95%e9%bb%9e%e4%ba%ae%e7%a7%8b/</link>
		
